Jo tich ma oriwore ma oa bad sirikal ma ochuungne loso yore madongo e Kenya ka - Kenya National Highway Authority (KeNHA), jogo ma osomo gero yore ma tiyo gi sirikal mar gweng’ ma Nakuru kod jogo ma osomo weche mag pimo kaka gedo owinjore obedi kamoro amora e piny nyocha odhi owuotho e kama owinjore ogere wang’ayo no.
